Description: Thank you for visiting our ebay store! Our tech-savvy E-GO Collection of bags lets you safely carry all your "tech-accessories" and look terrific doing it! This Laptop Career Bag means business. Protect your laptop and look your best. The top quality, weather-resistant, all leather construction is designed with strategic protection for all of your electronic essentials. There is a padded compartment for a laptop, tablet, reader or similar devices and other interior compartments to protect smart phone and music player. The top zipper closure helps to secure electronics and personal belongings and an inside zipper pocket for passport and personal items. The outside zipper pocket allows for quick access of items. An additional key keeper and convenient ID tag and protective cloth storage bag helps you keep organized and your Jill-e bag well protected. The comfortable handles feature a 8.5-Inch drop and offer a convenient and comfortable carrying option. What fits inside: Up to 12-Inch laptop computer and a protective insert for DSLR and 1-2 moderately sized lenses. Or many combinations of smaller items including laptop, reader and compact camera plus notebook, water bottle, umbrella, flip-flops, healthy snacks and wallet, keys, make-up, hair brush, hand sanitizer, tin of mints all your lifestyle essentials.
